== Net::OperaLink ==

A set of Perl classes to interface to the Opera Link API.

== What is the Opera Link API ? ==

http://www.opera.com/docs/apis/linkrest/

== Example of usage ==

Check out bin/link-api-example for an example.

== The code ==

Opera Software github repository, http://github.com/operasoftware/perl5-net-operalink

